  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add diced onion, carrot, and celery; sauté until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Stir in minced garlic and cook for 30 seconds until fragrant.",
    "Add tofu cubes, breaking them gently, and toast until golden on all sides, about 4 minutes.",
    "Whisk in tomato paste, smoked paprika, cumin, and chili powder; cook for 1 minute to bloom the spices.",
    "Pour in vegetable broth, bring to a gentle simmer, and let it reduce slightly for 8 minutes.",
    "Stir in coconut milk and lemon juice; continue simmering for 10 minutes until the bisque thickens and flavors meld.",
    "Use an immersion blender to purée the mixture until silky smooth, or transfer in batches to a stand blender; if desired, strain for extra creaminess.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste; gently reheat if necessary.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with chopped cilantro.",
    ""
